must be received by October 31, 2011 when review begins. No applications 
or dossier materials will be accepted after November 11, 2011. Questions 
may be sent through the Academic Careers website (<a href="http://tinyurl.com/4396x7x" rel="external">http://tinyurl.com/4396x7x</a>) 
(preferred) or <a href="mailto:philosophy_searches@lists.uchicago.edu" rel="email">philosophy_searches@lists.uchicago.edu</a> 
